00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:10,960
is that this isn't just a metaphor for paint.

18
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:12,100
No, not at all.

19
00:01:12,160 --> 00:01:15,700
It's the dominant metaphor for what is happening to human thought.

20
00:01:15,860 --> 00:01:15,960
Yeah.

21
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:22,720
So if you're listening to this and you've ever used an AI to draft an email or maybe a cover letter or a project proposal,

22
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:26,760
and you looked at the result and thought, wow, this sounds incredibly corporate and bland.

23
00:01:27,140 --> 00:01:28,920
Like, is this what my brain is turning into?

